# JAVA-Project

A simple Java-based application built for learning and practicing core Java, servlets, JSP, and JDBC integration.

## 🚀 Features

- Java Servlet-based backend
- JSP pages for dynamic content
- JDBC connectivity for database operations
- Folder structure follows standard Java web application conventions

## 🛠 Technologies Used

- Java
- JSP & Servlets
- JDBC
- MySQL / Oracle (choose your DB)
- Apache Tomcat (or any servlet container)

